'''Peter King Nzioki Mwania''' (yavutse 25 Gicurasi 1978), uzwi cyane nka '''Peter King''', ni umukinnyi wa firime muri  [[Kenya]] . <ref>http://www.spla.pro/en/file.person.peter-king-nzioki.35012.html</ref> <ref name=":0">https://www.pulse.ng/entertainment/movies/the-ceo-ive-been-an-actor-all-these-years-no-one-noticed-peter-king-says/36r7knj</ref> Azwi cyane ku ruhare rwe muri filime ''The Constant Gardener'',''The Fifth Estate'' and ''Sense8''. . <ref name=":0" />

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Nzioki yavutse ku ya 25 Gicurasi 1978 i Nairobi, muri [[Kenya]]. Se wa Michael David Mwania, yakoraga mu gisirikare cya Kenya naho nyina akora mu bitaro bya gisirikare. Afite imyaka itandatu, yinjiye mu rusengero mu kigo cya Lang'ata. Amashuri ye yarangije ayisumbuye muri Lang'ata i Nairobi. <ref name="kenyabuzz">https://www.kenyabuzz.com/lifestyle/hot-peter-king-mwania/</ref>

Yashakanye na mugenzi we bakina filime Tess King. <ref>https://www.myheritage.com/research/record-10182-2638546/peter-king-nzioki-in-biographical-summaries-of-notable-people</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Yatangiye gukina filime mu 2000 muri Theatre yigihugu ya Kenya imyaka itatu iyobowe na Joab Kanuka. Mu ikinamico, yakinnye 'Iago' muri Phoenix Players yerekana ibyago bya Shakespeare ''Othello'' . Muri 2005, yakinnye bwa mbere muri firime afite uruhare ruto muri ''[[The Constant Gardener (film)|The Constant Gardener]]'' iyobowe na Fernando Meirelles .  Muri uwo mwaka, yagaragaye nka 'Barman' muri televiziyo ya ''Transit'' . Muri 2016, yagaragaye muri firime ishimishije ''Umuyobozi mukuru'' aho yakinnye nka 'Jomo'. Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere ku ya 10 Nyakanga 2016, muri Eko Hotels & Suites, Ikirwa cya Victoria, Lagos <ref>http://thenet.ng/2016/07/kunle-afolayans-ceo-movie-to-premiere-in-lagos-today/</ref> nyuma iza gukundwa cyane. <ref name=":0" /> <ref>https://www.bellanaija.com/2016/07/chioma-nnanna-reviews-kunle-afolayans-new-movie-the-c-e-o/</ref> <ref>http://pulse.ng/movies/pulse-movie-review-kunle-afolayans-the-ceo-isnt-a-conventional-nollywood-movie-id5302986.html</ref>

Yagaragaye cyane nka 'Mkwajo' muri muzika ''Mo Faya'' yatsindiye ibihembo iyobowe na Eric Wainaina; umugambi ''mubisha muri FaceBook'' numunyapolitiki ruswa 'Mzito' muri ''Ni Sisi'' . Nyuma yinshingano nyinshi zubugome, yahawe umwanya wo kuba papa muri ''serivise ya'' MTV Shuga 2, hanyuma aba umutoza wumupira wamaguru muri ''The Inside Story'' yerekanwe kuri Discovery Channel; n'umuvugabutumwa mu ''Cyuma Cyuma Cyuma'' . <ref>https://www.kenyabuzz.com/lifestyle/hot-peter-king-mwania/</ref>

